Package: martin
Type: Package
Title: SIBYL Wrapper Around the bimets Implementation of MARTIN
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Stephan", email = "david.stephan@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Wraps the bimets implementation of the RBA's MARTIN
    macroeconometric model. Takes a starting database, exogenous paths, and a
    list of add-factors (from package judgement) keyed by equation and
    horizon; returns a solved projection as a tidy data frame.
    The bimets model definition files (MARTINMOD*.txt) and a frozen data
    fixture (MARTINDATA_XLSX) are vendored into inst/extdata/ from
    references/bimets-main/ with attribution.
